---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GitHubUser from "../components/GitHubUser.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="Drill"
	description="Drill is a modern, open-source alternative to OptiFine for NeoForge."
	style="drill"
>
	<img
		alt="Drill logo"
		src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/skywardmc/art/refs/heads/main/drill/logo_vector.svg"
		class="not-prose ms-4 float-end size-24 sm:size-32 rounded-sm"
	/>
	<section class="prose prose-skywardmc dark:prose-invert max-w-full">
		<p>
			Drill is a modpack, developed for NeoForge, designed as an alternative to
			OptiFine.
		</p>
		<p>
			This project is a port of <a href="/additive">Additive</a> to NeoForge. It uses
			<a href="https://sinytra.org/">Sinytra</a> along with native Forge ports. If
			you don't need any mods from NeoForge, we recommend that you use Adrenaline
			instead, as it has more features and better performance. This project is primarily
			focused for modpack creators.
		</p>
		<p>
			Drill's wiki is currently a work-in-progress. For more information, read
			through Drill's <a href="https://modrinth.com/project/drill">Modrinth</a> page.
		</p>
	</section>
	<p class="mt-4 text-sm flex items-center justify-end gap-1">
		Maintained by <GitHubUser user="omo50" class="font-bold" /> and <GitHubUser
			user="MenacingPerson"
			class="font-bold"
		/>
	</p>
</Layout>
